headline: Kenvue Increases Quarterly Cash Dividend
summary: SUMMIT, N.J., July 30, 2025--Kenvue Inc. (NYSE: KVUE) today announced its Board of Directors declared a quarterly dividend of $0.2075 per share on its common stock, which represents a 1.2 percent increase compared to the prior quarterly dividend. The quarterly dividend is payable on August 27, 2025, to shareholders of record as of the close of business on August 13, 2025.
